companyName: First Trust Dorsey Wright International Focus 5
description:
The investment seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield (before fees and expenses) of an index called the Dorsey Wright International Focus Five Index.
 The fund will normally invest at least 90% of its net assets (including investment borrowings) in the ETFs that comprise the index. The ETFs in which the fund invests are advised by First Trust Advisors L.P., the fund's investment advisor. The index is designed to provide targeted exposure to the five First Trust country/region-based ETFs that the index provider believes offer the greatest potential to outperform the other ETFs in the selection universe. It is non-diversified.
